Titolo: Ayakashi Ninden Kunoichiban

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: Ayakashi Ninden Kunoichiban (あやかし忍伝くの一番) is a Japanese dating sim by Shoeisha, released on March 14, 1997, for Windows 95 in Japan. A  PlayStation, and Sega Saturn version were soon released as well. It is a female ninja dating sim, as well as a gal game. It is said that the lesbian elements appear to be stronger in the PlayStation version.